item.title: CVE-2023-34394|2023-07-19T21:55:31.934Z -- keysight%20technologies -- n6845a%20geolocation%20server
item.description: In Keysight Geolocation Server v2.4.2 and prior, an attacker could upload a specially crafted malicious file or delete any file or directory with SYSTEM privileges due to an improper path validation, which could result in local privilege escalation or a denial-of-service condition.
